text.section:
The board shall, by administrative regulation promulgated in accordance with KRS Chapter 13A, prescribe a schedule of reasonable fees, charges, and fines not to exceed the national average of other state dental boards for:
Examination;
Issuance, renewal, and reinstatement of licenses;
Issuance, renewal, and reinstatement of registrations;
Inspections and reinspections;
Applications;
Other services and materials provided by the board;
Investigations;
Administrative legal costs; and
Fines for infractions.
